"{\n  \"correct\": \"no\",\n  \"explanation\": \"The code is using sns.lmplot inside sns.FacetGrid.map, which is incorrect. The sns.FacetGrid.map function is used to apply a plotting function to each facet of the grid. However, sns.lmplot is a high-level interface for drawing attractive and informative statistical graphics and it itself creates a FacetGrid. Therefore, it cannot be used inside another FacetGrid.\",\n  \"patch\": \"5,7c5,7\\n< g = sns.FacetGrid(data=tips, col='time', row='sex')\\n< g.map(sns.lmplot, 'total_bill', 'tip')\\n---\\n> g = sns.lmplot(data=tips, x='total_bill', y='tip', col='time', row='sex')\\n\"\n}"